name: Necromancy Style
description:
This is a new direction for me! A very dark embedding with a theme of necromancy; skulls, the living dead, and dark magic! It pairs really well with my other styles to produce some outrageously good effects!

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Necromancy - see the images below. Mostly, you'll need to reduce the strength of Necromancy - it comes through pretty strongly.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
